    "description": "<p>You have completely mastered the wolf within. You can transform one additional time without suffering a level of fatigue.</p><p>When you choose to tame the beast in an involuntary transformation, roll 1d8; you gain control over that many hours. While you are transformed, you gain the following features.</p><p><strong><em>Cursed Wounds.</em></strong> Your bite and claw attacks both deal an additional 1d6 necrotic damage.</p><p><strong><em>Full Moon Defense.</em></strong> You gain immunity against slashing, bludgeoning, and piercing damage from weapons that are not magical or silvered.</p><p><strong><em>Heightened Senses.</em></strong> You gain an expertise die on Perception checks.</p>",
